<li><a href="http://www.unhchr.ch/html/menu3/b/k2crc.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.unhchr.ch/html/menu3/b/k2crc.htm" rel="nofollow">Text of the UN Convention on the Rights of the Child</a></li>
