<li><a href="http://www.unicef.org/specialsession/how_country/index.html" class="external text" title="http://www.unicef.org/specialsession/how_country/index.html" rel="nofollow">Results of the convention - National Action Plans of the ratifiyng countries</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.canadiancrc.com" class="external text" title="http://www.canadiancrc.com" rel="nofollow">Canadian Children's Rights Council - Conseil canadien des droits des enfants</a></li>
